title: Robert Plant  -  Lullaby..... And The Ceaseless Roar   2014
description:
Robert Plant  -  Lullaby..... And The Ceaseless Roar transcode  2014  What we got...            Lullaby and... The Ceaseless Roar is English rock singer Robert Plant's tenth solo album and the first studio one with his backing band The Sensational Space Shifters, although the name of the band is not mentioned in the front cover. It will be released on 8 September 2014 on Nonesuch/Bros. Records.
